      <h4>Your Input</h4>
      <p>Most importantly: Your input. How long you are going, for what purpose, etc.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="landing-value" style="margin: 0px">
    <%= cl_image_tag "weather.svg", width: 100, crop: :fill %>
